{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2959333, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "支持dz", "timestamp": 1637079326, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959341, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他大概率醒不过来了。一辈子没有收入，怎么养活？\n一堆烂人哔哔哔", "timestamp": 1637079349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959341, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 唉，别这么说", "timestamp": 1637079390, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959363, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959341, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 希望这位同学能醒过来吧", "timestamp": 1637079403, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959418, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959363, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 出血量太大了。", "timestamp": 1637079529, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959427, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不公开财产就理应收到必要的质疑", "timestamp": 1637079551, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959341, "tag": null, "text": "真的是觉得太惨了，管他家里几千万，我给他十块钱也不痛不痒，同学一场", "timestamp": 1637079582, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959446, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959427, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 理应xxx", "timestamp": 1637079603, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959548, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959446, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 难道不理应吗 我确实和他同学一场，但是他的家长应该对我们的善意负责，至少应该信息透明化", "timestamp": 1637079913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959548, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: “应该”“应该”，这个应该是法律义务吗？不是。是道德要求吗？也许是，道德要求有强制力吗？没有。", "timestamp": 1637080056, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 话是这么说，但是如果你发现受捐人实际没到山穷水尽的地步，是会影响你下一次对这种不公示财产人的猜忌的。一定程度上也会阻碍一部分人之后继续参与这种募捐", "timestamp": 1637080590, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959789, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 算我表达有偏差而你抓的重点也错了", "timestamp": 1637080681, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959821, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 没有强制力，确实。也没人能强制得动他。\n但是我们呼吁一个没有强制要求的事情，有问题吗？我们的呼吁是为了保证每一个需要帮助的人都可以被放心帮助，而你的呼吁是在减弱他们被帮助的机会。", "timestamp": 1637080846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959828, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 561684, "reply_to": 2959341, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 话说的难听但是事实。而且昏迷两个月以上就算醒来也能恢复有限了，身边例子，自理都难", "timestamp": 1637080867, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 561684, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "想给今天热议的筹款问题提供个新思路哈\n我个人倾向于他家真的遇到了经济困难，钱花完了也好，来不及卖房也好，生意周转不开也好，总之有原因的。\n毕竟只筹80万，如果像某些人说的那样，他家特别有钱，80万应该不值得这么干。\n因为诈捐这个事情属实是缺了大德了，在儿子生命垂危的时候，平时再不迷信的人也会想积点德的。\n而且这个同学是南方人，那边整体似乎是比较迷信一点的【没有地图炮别杠】", "timestamp": 1637079296, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637080870, "url": "", "vote": {}}}